&lt;li&gt;Assist in Room Service if needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist other restaurant personnel with tasks when necessary such as expediting food to tables.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional projects and responsibilities may be assigned as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1 year of experience in a similar or supportive role in an upscale environment is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food Handler Certification (If applicable).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and conduct multiple tasks in a dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hardworking, dedicated, with a real passion for hospitality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of or ability to learn the restaurant point of sale system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position requires a flexible schedule, must be able to work evenings, weekends, and holidays.&lt;/li&gt;
